
THIS FILE IS AN EXPLANATION OF THE FILES 
created by Denis McGonigal


AC4.lisp : contains the lisp code for the AC4 algorithm by Mohr & Henderson.
AC4test  : contains the test input and test calls for the AC4 algorithm
ChoprasAC4 : contains code for AC4 sent by E-mail, the input format in unkown
Hany : E-mail file mentioning problems with AC-4
acq.lisp : contains lisp code for fractional arc consistency algorithms
step.lisp : contains test code for step1 of AC4, gives a formatted output
temp-queens-lists : contains test input and test calls for acq.lisp algorithms
